flowchart TD
    A[Admin writes blog in frontend] --> B[POST or PUT /api/blogs]
    B --> C[Backend validates payload]
    C --> D[Convert content_html to content_text]
    D --> E[Save blog in Postgres]

    E --> F{Is status published?}
    F -- No --> G[Keep as draft in Postgres]
    F -- Yes --> H[Set index_status to pending]
    H --> I[Enqueue blog in IndexingService]

    I --> J[Load published blog from Postgres]
    J --> K[Chunk plain text into smaller sections]
    K --> L[Generate embeddings with OpenAI]
    L --> M[Replace blog chunks in Qdrant]
    M --> N[Mark index_status ready]

    O[User asks question in frontend] --> P[POST /api/ask]
    P --> Q[Normalize question and tags]
    Q --> R[Generate question embedding]
    R --> S[Search nearest chunks in Qdrant]
    S --> T[Filter by published status and optional tags]
    T --> U[Group top hits by blog]
    U --> V[Build grounded context from snippets]
    V --> W[Ask OpenAI to answer from context only]
    W --> X[Return answer with citations]

    G -. Drafts are not retrievable .-> O
    N -. Published blogs become retrievable .-> O
